{
  "stem": "23278.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They knew other teachers in other city, created some sort of a net.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's how Rita really could manage to go to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was not through me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was through the teachers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And our principal, who had been a lecturer at Bryn Mawr, an instructor in Bryn Mawr, and was now the-- you know, a high school in France is not a high school here.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It is very academic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was you had an exam before you entered.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was like the gymnasium in Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She was a very educated woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she died in Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She was Catholic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she was involved in mostly rescuing pilots, British or American pilots who, you know, had to fall with a parachute and had to be taken care of.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She was given away, and she died in Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was-- somebody informed on her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was an informer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she took-- she took care of a lot of Jews too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, when people took care of Jews, it was not because they were Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's because they were persecuted people and because the Nazi wanted them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was all a very loose thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody gave their name to anybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because in case you be caught, you would talk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That they left?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were told that the-- yeah, but we felt that they were going in a safe place, that they were going to the South, and they were going to the country.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like our protestant ancestor, they were going somewhere where they wouldn't be caught.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, quite a few came back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Except one, except one-- and that is a very sad story.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the story of Beatrice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Beatrice came from Germany, from [NON-ENGLISH], And then she came to Alsace.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
